'''Anasakti Yoga''' is a way of life described by [[Mahatma Gandhi]]. He translated the Slokas of [[Bhagavad Gita]] and named it ''Anasakti Yoga''.<ref>http://www.mkgandhi.org/swmgandhi/chap01.htm</ref>

