'''''Lumen Veritatis''''' is a quarterly [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] published by the St. Thomas Aquinas Institute of Theology and the Aristotelian-Thomistic Institute of Philosophy in Brazil. Its covers the study of [[theology]] and [[philosophy]] in a [[Thomism|Thomistic]] perspective in a critical dialogue with other philosophical schools.

