'''Sangpo Bumtri''' ({{bo|w=sangs po bum 'khri}}) is the creator god of [[Bon]].<ref name="kværne-1995"/> He has "neither eyes to see, nor hands to hold, nor ears to hear, or nose to smell, he has only his spirit".<ref name="grutschke-2000"/>
